    <text>Looks after a representation of a block stack. Manages both stand alone and sub-block
stacks. If a sub-block stack, then the bypassedControllers list is populated with the
location controllers that this object has assumed control over.
Text Class CM_BlockController We create a location for each tracked item in the block stack.</text>
